summary: THQ Nordic Is Teasing Two Unannounced Games That Will Be Revealed At E3 2019
title: THQ Nordic Is Teasing Two Unannounced Games That Will Be Revealed At E3 2019
body:
THQ Nordic Is Teasing Two Unannounced Games That Will Be Revealed At E3 2019

E3 2019 is less than a month away, so the pre-E3 news cycle is in full swing. THQ Nordichave sent an email to the press that talks about their plans for E3. The email teased two games that will not be announced until E3. The first one is a “remake”, and it will be “the long-awaited return of a galactically beloved game/franchise”. The second game is “a new vision of a beloved game/franchise”.…

summary: ASSASSIN'S CRED \ Hotline Miami 2: Wrong Number
title: ASSASSIN'S CRED \ Hotline Miami 2: Wrong Number
description:
ASSASSIN’S CRED is an achievement in Hotline Miami 2: Wrong Number.

To unlock this achievement, the player must kill all enemies on the first floor of No Mercy using only The Henchman’s silenced pistol.

Methods

The silenced pistol contains 12 shots and there are exactly 12 enemies to kill. Therefore, missing a shot means you will have to start over.

The best method for unlocking the achievement is to play the level on normal and use lock-on (middle mouse button). Proceed through the section of the level with caution and try to take out the gang members one at a time or in a controlled manner. Trivia

The name of the achievement is an obvious reference to the Assassin’s Creed series.

Bugs

This achievement is unobtainable if completed on hard, only on normal will the achievement be granted.
